3458.Name: 2021/2022 Paddle Club Championships
3458.WaiverText:
BY ALLOWING MY NAME TO APPEAR ON Congressional In-House Paddle League, I and my partner agree to abide by all rules of Congressional In-House Paddle League . I do hereby and on behalf of myself and my partner, heirs and legal representatives release and forever discharge Congressional In-House Paddle League of and from any and all claims and demands of every kind, nature and character which I or my partner may have or may hereafter acquire for any and all damages, losses or injuries which may be suffered or sustained by me or my partner. I and my partner also understand that any special medical needs remain the responsibility of the individual player.
I and my partner hereby grant Congressional In-House Paddle League permission to use our likeness in photograph(s)/video in any and all of its media, publications, whether now known or hereafter existing, controlled by Congressional In-House Paddle League, in perpetuity, and for other use by Congressional In-House Paddle League.  I and my partner will make no monetary or other claim against Congressional In-House Paddle League for the use of such photograph(s)/video.
